OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShowery outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fspreading east through the morning.
OL,7,FTurning brighter later in the
OL,8,Fafternoon with some sunnier spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping and showers becoming fewer.
OL,10,FBreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLate sunny spells as showers
OL,13,Fclear away this evening. The rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will see mostly dry
OL,15,Fconditions, perhaps the odd light
OL,16,Fshower in the west. Patchy rural frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
