OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FRather cloudy, especially
OL,6,Faround northern coasts where they'll
OL,7,Fbe a few showers, these perhaps
OL,8,Fspreading south later. Breezy on
OL,9,Fcoasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRather
OL,12,Fcloudy on Monday with a few showery
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain spreading south.
OL,14,FMainly dry and bright on Tuesday and
OL,15,FWednesday, but the east coast
OL,16,Fgenerally cloudier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
